    "title": "Job Opening Hotel Manager at Zomato Restaurant Partners Consulting Pvt Ltd",
    "description": "Grow your career with Zomato Restaurant Partners Consulting Pvt Ltd! We are hiring a Hotel Manager for our Pimpri-Chinchwad team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Zomato Restaurant Partners Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nZomato Restaurant Partners Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Flexible working hours\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pimpri-Chinchwad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zomato Restaurant Partners Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
